      "title": "Sri Lanka shares gain over 1-pct in mid-day trade",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "ECONOMYNEXT \u2013 Sri Lanka shares gained over 1 percent within the first hour of trade on Monday (22), Colombo Stock Exchange data showed.",
        "The main All Share Price Index moved up 114.66 points or 1.28 percent to 9,090.41 at 1130 hours.",
        "The most liquid index S&P SL20 moved up 48.11 points or 1.62 percent to 3,012.06."
      ],
